text:
STR3AMING GUIDELINES! (TAKE NOTE! COMEBACK IS NEAR)
- Search the mv MANUALLY! (ex. NCT - “mv title”) 
- Watch MV till the end ( at least 720 p or higher!)
- Volume can be on any level but don’t mute!
- Share link on your sns (fb, twitter, ig, etc.)
- LOG IN to like and comment but LOG OUT while streaming because it will make things easier and you don’t have to change accounts (BUT it is also okay to str3am while logged in)
- Use the words str3am or str3aming only when commenting
- DON’T use a playlist during the 24 hours! after 24 hours, it’s okay :)
- DON’T use multiple tabs If you’re on your laptop/pc, use browsers instead. 
- DON’T skip ads
- CLEAR browser cookies and history often! (i recommend at least every 30min)
- DON’T replay or watch the mv over and over again! after watching it, watch 3-4 videos in betweeen before watching it again (because yt counts those as spam, they’ll get deleted and the views feeze)
- DON’T str3am continuously/loop
- DON’T comment with emojis
- DON’T speed up the mv
- DON’T pause or stop the video! watch the whole video and don’t rewind.
- DON’T use incognito mode
- DON’T use bots/extensions to increase views

For sure the views will freeze but don’t mind it! continue str3aming it will be counted as long as you str3am correctly. LET’S WORK HARD FOR THE BOYS! (yall are free to copy this and share it to other nctzens!)
